AOIDE DAC DRIVERS FOR Raspberry PI

AOIDE DAC Pro
AOIDE DAC II
AOIDE Digi Pro
AOIDE Zero DAC+
AOIDE ZPOD DAC
Raspi Voice HAT  

www.aoide.cc

For Raspbian,Raspberry OS,DietPI
git clone https://github.com/u-geek/aoide-dac-drivers.git
cd aoide-dac-drivers
sudo ./dac_install.sh

    ┌────────┤ AOIDE DAC Drivers Installer(V4.19.118) ├────────┐
    │ Select your DAC(Sound Card).                             │
    │                                                          │
    │                    1 AOIDE DAC Pro                       │
    │                    2 AOIDE DAC II                        │
    │                    3 AOIDE Digi Pro                      │
    │                    4 AOIDE Zero DAC+                     │
    │                    5 AOIDE ZPOD DAC                      │
    │                    6 Raspi Voice HAT                     │
    │                    D Disable DAC                         │
    │                    E Exit                                │
    │                                                          │
    │                                                          │
    │                                                          │
    │              <Ok>                  <Exit>                │
    │                                                          │
    └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

For Aoide TFT Screen based on raspbian
curl -L --output ./aoidetft_setup.sh https://github.com/u-geek/aoide-dac-drivers/raw/master/aoidetft_setup.sh && chmod +x ./aoidetft_setup.sh
sudo ./aoidetft_setup.sh

For Aoide TFT Screen based on retropie
curl -L --output ./aoiderp_setup.sh https://github.com/u-geek/aoide-dac-drivers/raw/master/aoiderp_setup.sh && chmod +x ./aoiderp_setup.sh
sudo ./aoiderp_setup.sh
